      "content": "\"Surrender to the void\"... that's exactly what it feels like. It sounds almost peaceful, in a dark way. Like the exhaustion of trying to maintain a facade is finally over and there's nothing left to do but just... stop. Is that what you're saying? That the only real way to find peace is to just stop trying to exist in this world?",
